{
  "stem": "1502.2",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And we could not go out in the streets, because there was bombing and shooting very often.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "I remember I was standing in line to get bread, and bombs were falling.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "I had to take cover somewhere in a basement.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And finally, the shooting and the bombing stopped.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And the French had surrendered the city to the Germans.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "We were very scared of what's going to happen next.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "We had a balcony on the-- on one of the main streets in Lille, and matter of fact, the main street.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And we saw-- at first, the streets were empty.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "There wasn't a soul.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "There was no one in the streets.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "It was early in the morning, and we saw the first Germans coming into the city.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "They came on bicycles.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "It was like the-- the front runners, the-- the-- before-- those patrols that came before the Army.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "It was the first time in my life that I saw German soldiers.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And we-- we were very scared.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "Then, a few hours later, we saw thousands, or tens of thousands, of German and British prisoners that they walked back to Germany to prison camps.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "Were surrounded with German guards.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And still, there were no people daring going-- to go out in the street.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "I remember the first contact we had with the Germans.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "It was-- and so we were in the hotel, and we had the balcony.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "We were on a low floor.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "And we-- there was knocking on the door, and they were German soldiers.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "They asked us if we would-- politely-- if we would let them install wires on the balcony.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "They had to make-- they were communications soldiers.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "They wanted to establish communication with their headquarters.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "Of course, we let them-- we let them in.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
